# Premium Cinematic Typography Overhaul

Upgrade the application's font system from standard "Inter" to a high-end, cinematic pairing of **Bebas Neue** (for aggressive, condensed display headers) and **Outfit** (for premium geometric body text).

## Proposed Changes

### [Layout & Theme]
- **[MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/layout.tsx)**: Remove Inter; import `Outfit` and `Bebas_Neue` from `next/font/google`.
- **[MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///C:/GOLive/app/globals.css)**: 
    - Update `--font-sans` to use `Outfit`.
    - Add `--font-display` using `Bebas_Neue`.
    - Adjust letter-spacing for premium feel.

### [Component Updates]
- **[MODIFY] [Navbar.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/Navbar.tsx)**: Apply Display font to the "GoLive" brand logo.
- **[MODIFY] [HomeClient.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/HomeClient.tsx)**: Apply Display font to section headings and "FEATURED PREMIERE".
- **[MODIFY] [login/page.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/login/page.tsx)** & **[register/page.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/register/page.tsx)**: Unified typography for "BREACH PROTOCOL" headers.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `npm run build` to ensure font optimization works correctly.

### Manual Verification
- Visual inspection of contrast, readability, and "premium" factor across all pages.
- Verify no "cheap" appearance in input fields or secondary meta data.
